{"tid":782554,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"dual mon 2nd mon 玩遊戲鎖住左係60fps,求救","createTime":"2018-08-16T23:55:20.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-18T14:47:05.000Z","uid":58425,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"5e2186cfc7aa3c9073fdd9c1d0b6d6e70c9ea8f5","tid":782554,"uid":58425,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-16T23:55:20.000Z","msg":"我有2個mon,<br />\n一個PG248Q (144Hz, 2k), 一個PB279Q (60fps,4k)<br />\n<br />\n當PG248Q做次要mon<br />\n而又係extend monitor嘅時候,玩任何GAME都係得60fps<br />\n但轉primary mon, duplicate mon 就出到144fps<br />\n<br />\n而另一個MON PB279Q 無論extend, duplicate, primary,secondary 既時候玩GAME都可以144fps<br />\n<br />\n重申係game 144fps 唔係monitor 144Hz<br />\n試過轉monitor refresh rate, 熄v sync, 去過window advace graphic setting 轉refresh rate 都唔成功<br />\n<br />\n有冇高人知點解<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"67c5f67a1e6f5814b00a3723d63b554362e960c2","tid":782554,"uid":113776,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-17T00:10:05.000Z","msg":"搭單問一問，我打機出唔到兩個mon，有無可能notebook mon加外接mon一齊出？"},{"pid":"2fa557627a0fd84409665c09cb60edaf6f87c95f","tid":782554,"uid":61689,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"67c5f67a1e6f5814b00a3723d63b554362e960c2","tid":782554,"uid":113776,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-17T00:10:05.000Z","msg":"搭單問一問，我打機出唔到兩個mon，有無可能notebook mon加外接mon一齊出？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-17T00:22:00.000Z","msg":"可以<br />\n右下角度set平行"},{"pid":"c3230e3829536b0a71f9aff528b8049413277ed5","tid":782554,"uid":30686,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-17T00:52:22.000Z","msg":"咪就係去1 mon 嘅signal限左去2 mon 嘅signal囉"},{"pid":"fed233f4b8710260007ed1506aa09d0ef8eb42a4","tid":782554,"uid":113776,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2fa557627a0fd84409665c09cb60edaf6f87c95f","tid":782554,"uid":61689,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"67c5f67a